data.description: Welcome to 1149 Trolling Drive, a beautiful and spacious home nestled in the heart of Apopka, FL. This beautiful 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom  Solar Powered home features an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or spending time with family. The kitchen boasts*Stainless Steel* appliances, ample*Granite Counter* space, and a breakfast bar, making it the ideal spot for whipping up your culinary delights. Downstairs also boast a bedroom and full bathroom with stand in shower.     Upstairs includes the remaining bedrooms, laundry room and a spacious loft that could be used as a secondary family room or game room. The primary bedroom is a peaceful oasis with an*En-suite Bathroom* and an extra large*Walk-in Closet*. The other bedrooms are bright and airy, offering plenty of space for relaxation, study or work office. The home also features a covered lanai, providing a perfect spot for enjoying the beautiful Florida weather. Located in the highly desirable Rock Springs neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from shopping, dining, and entertainment options.
